data.description: Welcome home to this fabulous ranch in Greenwood's desirable Honey Creek Meadows subdivision! With 1609 square feet of living space, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem is perfect for entertaining. The Clark-Pleasant School System is just one of the many outstanding features of this home. Step inside to discover the 9' ceilings and the spacious open floor plan. The kitchen boasts 42" maple cabinets and a bonus breakfast bar top, perfect for gatherings and entertaining. The primary bedroom offers a double sink vanity, while the secondary bedrooms are generously sized. Enjoy the large fully fenced rear yard, providing privacy and a safe space for outdoor activities. With its low-maintenance vinyl/brick exterior and highly desired split bedroom design, this home truly offers the best of comfort and convenience. No down payment program may be available. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity!
